{"collections":[{"id":"ukcp","description":"Regional climate model projections produced as part of the UK Climate Projection 2018 (UKCP18) project. The data produced by the Met Office Hadley Centre provides information on changes in climate for the UK until 2080, downscaled to a high resolution (12km), helping to inform adaptation to a changing climate. The projections cover Europe and a 100 year period, 1981-2080, for a high emissions scenario, RCP8.5. Each projection provides an example of climate variability in a changing climate, which is consistent across climate variables at different times and spatial locations. This dataset contains 12km data for the United Kingdom, the Isle of Man and the Channel Islands provided on the Ordnance Survey's British National Grid.","stac_version":"1.0.0","links":[{"rel":"items","type":"application/geo+json","href":"https://eodatahub.org.uk/api/catalogue/stac/catalogs/public/catalogs/ceda-stac-catalogue/collections/ukcp/items"},{"rel":"parent","type":"application/json","href":"https://eodatahub.org.uk/api/catalogue/stac/catalogs/public/catalogs/ceda-stac-catalogue"},{"rel":"root","type":"application/json","href":"https://eodatahub.org.uk/api/catalogue/stac/"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/json","href":"https://eodatahub.org.uk/api/catalogue/stac/catalogs/public/catalogs/ceda-stac-catalogue/collections/ukcp"},{"href":"https://catalogue.ceda.ac.uk/uuid/589211abeb844070a95d061c8cc7f604","rel":"ceda_catalogue","type":"text/html"}],"stac_extensions":[],"title":"UK Climate Projections (UKCP18)","type":"Collection","assets":{"thumbnail":{"href":"https://dap.ceda.ac.uk/badc/ukcp18/metadata/STAC/ukcp18_thumbnail.png","type":"image/png","roles":["thumbnail"]}},"license":"OGL-UK-3.0","extent":{"spatial":{"bbox":[[-12.773760091513395,49.313714699819684,3.4064378030598164,60.526678590103984]]},"temporal":{"interval":[["2060-12-01T12:00:00Z","2080-11-30T12:00:00Z"]]}},"keywords":["UK","Climate","Projections","UKCP18","Regional","Europe","